Purpose:

This script should handle most of the basic work of setting up a fresh install of Cent OS 5.X. It's been tested on CentOS 5.7 x86_64.

Requirements:

- perl 5.8

Usage:

./serverConfig.pl

Notes: 

- None yet.

Support / Help / Patches:

I'm very pleased to accept any patches / fixes / bugs. Drop me a 
note at linuxmofo007@gmail.com.

Versions:

0.1 - Setup basic server services, users, groups, permissions, start up apps
